Feature: Gateway

Scenario: Simple gateway
	When I start a service "#serviceFuture" with options:
		| option	 		| value |
		| withModule		| com.simplyti.service.gateway.GatewayModule |
		| withModule		| com.simplyti.service.discovery.TestServiceDiscoveryModule |
		| withLog4J2Logger	|		|
